==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Leveler
<hw>Lev"el*er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Written also
<ets>leveller</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which,
levels.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who would remove social inequalities or
distinctions; a socialist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>levelheaded</ent>⟦br⟧
